quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  64,1,Yusebbihu lillahi ma fiyssemavati ve ma fiylÂṀardÄḟ lehulmulku ve lehulhamdu ve huve ÂṀala kulli ÅeyÂṀin kadiyrun
  64,2,Huvelleziy halekakum feminkum kafirun ve minku muÂṀminun vallahu bima taÂṀmelune basÄḟyrun
  64,3,Halekassemavati velÂṀarda bilhakkÄḟ ve savverekum feahsene suverekum ve ileyhilmasÄḟyru
  64,4,YaÂṀlemu ma fiyssemavati velÂṀardÄḟ ve yaÂṀlemu ma tusirrune ve ma tuÂṀlinune vallahu ÂṀaliymun bizatissuduri
  64,5,Elem yeÂṀtikum nebeulleziyne keferu min kablu fezaku vebale emrihim ve lehum ÂṀazabun eliymun
  64,6,Zalike biennehu kanet teÂṀtiyhim rusuluhum bilbeyyinati fekalu ebeÅerun yehdunena fekeferu ve tevellev vestaÄnallahu vallahu ÄanÄḟyyun hamiydun
  64,7,ZeÂṀamelleziyne keferu en len yubÂṀasu kul bela ve rabbiy letubÂṀasunne summe letunebbeunne bima ÂṀamiltum ve zalike ÂṀalellahi yesiyrun
  64,8,Feaminu billahi ve resulihi vennurilleziy enzelna vallahu bima taÂṀmelune habiyrun
  64,9,Yevme yecmeÂṀukum liyevmicemÂṀÄḟ zalike yevmutteÄabuni ve men yuÂṀmin billahi ve yaÂṀmel salihan yukeffir ÂṀanhu seyyiatihi ve yudhÄḟlhu cennatin tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu halidiyne fiyha ebeden zalikelfevzulÂṀazÄḟymu